&lt;h1 id="american-spring"&gt;American Spring&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jan 15 2016&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A one party system ran the United States, and the United States ran the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The US had checks and balances – governing required consensus, and the people were freed from kings. To protect speech, the framers left out a rule against conspiracies to monopolize the vote.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>